#: ../plone_training_config/instructions.rst:119
msgid "Installing Plone with vagrant"
msgstr "Instalando Plone sin vagrant"

#: ../plone_training_config/instructions.rst:121
msgid ""
"In order not to waste too much time with installing and debugging the "
"differences between systems, we use a virtual machine (Ubuntu 14.04) to run "
"Plone during the training. We rely on Vagrant and VirtualBox to give the "
"same development environment to everyone."
msgstr ""
"Para no perder demasiado tiempo con la instalación y la depuración de las "
"diferencias entre los sistemas, utilizamos una máquina virtual (Ubuntu "
"14.04) para ejecutar Plone durante el entrenamiento. Contamos con Vagrant y "
"VirtualBox para dar el mismo medio de ambiente de desarrollo para todos."

#: ../plone_training_config/instructions.rst:123
msgid ""
"`Vagrant <https://www.vagrantup.com>`_ is a tool for building complete "
"development environments. We use it together with Oracle’s `VirtualBox "
"<https://www.virtualbox.org>`_ to create and manage a virtual environment."
msgstr ""
"`Vagrant <http://www.vagrantup.com>`_ es una herramienta para la creación de"
" entornos de desarrollo completos. Lo usamos en conjunto con Oracle’s "
"`VirtualBox <https://www.virtualbox.org>`_ para crear y administrar un "
"entorno virtual."

#: ../plone_training_config/instructions.rst:128
msgid "Install VirtualBox"
msgstr "Instalar VirtualBox"

